vue directives
--------------
  v-

v-text
v-html
v-show
v-if
v-else
v-else-if
v-for
v-on
v-bind
v-model
v-slot
v-pre
v-cloak
v-once

https://vuejs.org/v2/api/#Directives


conditional
v-if 
  <button v-if="userIsLoggedIn">Log Out</button>
  <button v-if="!userIsLoggedIn">Log In</button>

loop 
v-for 
  <ul>
    <li v-for="dog in doglist">{{ dog }}</li>
  </ul>

modify (and show) 'data.username' in options-object
  <input v-model="username" />

v-on 
  <button v-on:click="tweets.push(newTweet)"> Add Tweet </button>